unctional form for the NIR extinction law. In the\nappendix we detail the treatment of non-linear photometric effects in the 2MASS\nbands.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2020 14:42:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-01"}
